{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-1-to-100/problem-80-square-root-digital-expansion","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"project-euler-problems-1-to-100","demoType":null,"title":"Vežba 80: Razvijanje kvadratnog korena za brojeve","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Dobro je poznato da ako kvadratni koren prirodnog broja nije ceo broj, onda je iracionalan broj. Decimalno razvijanje takvog kvadratnog korena je beskonačno i nema nikakav ponavljajući obrazac.</p>\n<p>Koren iz dva je <code>1.41421356237309504880...</code>, a zbir prvih sto decimalnih cifara je <code>475</code>.</p>\n<p>Za originalni broj <code>n</code>, izračunaj ukupan zbir prvih sto decimalnih cifara za sve iracionalne korene.</p>\n</section>","id":"5900f3bc1000cf542c50fecf","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"","notes":null,"challengeType":1,"helpCategory":"Euler","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"project-euler","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":302194,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-1-to-100/problem-80-square-root-digital-expansion"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":false,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"scriptjs","ext":"js","name":"script","contents":"function sqrtDigitalExpansion(n) {\n\n  return true;\n}\n\nsqrtDigitalExpansion(2);","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[],"history":["script.js"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p><code>sqrtDigitalExpansion(2)</code> treba da vrati broj.</p>","testString":"assert(typeof sqrtDigitalExpansion(2) === 'number');"},{"text":"<p><code>sqrtDigitalExpansion(2)</code> treba da vrati <code>475</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.strictEqual(sqrtDigitalExpansion(2), 475);"},{"text":"<p><code>sqrtDigitalExpansion(50)</code> treba da vrati <code>19543</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.strictEqual(sqrtDigitalExpansion(50), 19543);"},{"text":"<p><code>sqrt